OL,3,CAcademics create smartwatch technology
OL,4,Cto help people quit smoking
OL,6,FTechnology in smartwatches could help
OL,7,Fpeople quit smoking, according to
OL,8,Fresearchers from the University of
OL,9,FBristol.
OL,11,FThe team created software that uses
OL,12,Fmotion sensors on an Android
OL,13,Fsmartwatch to identify the typical
OL,14,Fhand movements of smoking.
OL,16,FOnce detected, the app delivers a
OL,17,Fvibration alert with a text message
OL,18,Fdesigned by smokers and former
OL,19,Fsmokers, offering support to stop
OL,20,Fsmoking.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
