OL,3,CAcademics create smartwatch technology
OL,4,Cto help people quit smoking
OL,6,FAfter reading the message,
OL,7,Fparticipants can swipe it away or
OL,8,Fpress a button to access NHS support
OL,9,Fpages.
OL,11,FChris Stone, of the University of
OL,12,FBristol's Tobacco and Alcohol Research
OL,13,FGroup, said: "For those who are trying
OL,14,Fto give up, an initial lapse is a
OL,15,Fvulnerable moment, and risks leading
OL,16,Fto a full relapse to smoking.
OL,18,F"People like smartwatches. They like
OL,19,Fthe idea of it delivering a message at
OL,20,Fthe point that they smoke.
