OL,3,CAcademics create smartwatch technology
OL,4,Cto help people quit smoking
OL,6,F"Therefore, if we can identify this
OL,7,Fpoint of lapse, and deliver an
OL,8,Fintervention precisely at that point,
OL,9,Fwe have an opportunity to improve the
OL,10,Fsuccess of the quit attempt.
OL,12,F"In carrying out this project, we have
OL,13,Faimed to harness the latest thinking
OL,14,Fin intervention design, and deliver it
OL,15,Fin a convenient wearable package with
OL,16,Fminimal burden to the user and maximum
OL,17,Fengagement with behaviour change; and
OL,18,Fin doing so, make a difference to
OL,19,Fpeople's lives."
