OL,3,CAcademics create smartwatch technology
OL,4,Cto help people quit smoking
OL,6,FIn the study, published in JMIR
OL,7,FFormative Research, the smartwatch app
OL,8,Fwas tested on 18 people who were
OL,9,Finterested in quitting smoking.
OL,11,FAt the end of the two-week test
OL,12,Fperiod, they sent the watch back and
OL,13,Fcompleted a questionnaire.
OL,15,FPositive feedback included people
OL,16,Freporting that the app raised
OL,17,Fawareness of smoking, made them feel
OL,18,Fpositive about quitting, made them
OL,19,Fstop and think, smoke slightly less,
OL,20,Fand it provided constant encouragement.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
