OL,6,FNegative responses were that repeated
OL,7,Fmessages lost effectiveness, the
OL,8,Fmessage did not appear quickly enough,
OL,9,Fthere was not enough variety of
OL,10,Fmessages, and some were vague.
OL,12,FAlizee Froguel, prevention policy
OL,13,Fmanager at Cancer Research UK, said:
OL,14,F"Smoking is the biggest cause of
OL,15,Fcancer in the UK and stopping
OL,16,Fcompletely is the best thing you can
OL,17,Fdo for your health.
