OL,3,CAcademics create smartwatch technology
OL,4,Cto help people quit smoking
OL,6,F"This study shows that smartwatches
OL,7,Fcould be a useful method to help
OL,8,Fpeople quit smoking, but more research
OL,9,Fis needed to understand how effective
OL,10,Fthey are.
OL,12,F"There are many tools available to
OL,13,Fhelp people quit, and getting support
OL,14,Ffrom your free local stop smoking
OL,15,Fservice will give you the best chance
OL,16,Fof stopping successfully."
