OL,3,CAcademics create smartwatch technology
OL,4,Cto help people quit smoking
OL,6,FThe researchers believe their app is
OL,7,Fthe first just-in-time intervention
OL,8,Ffor preventing smoking relapse that
OL,9,Fruns entirely on a smartwatch and does
OL,10,Fnot need to be paired with a
OL,11,Fsmartphone.
OL,13,FThey are calling for a longer-term
OL,14,Feffectiveness trial to be carried out
OL,15,Fas the next step, which could use a
OL,16,Fgreater variety of messages.
